{"tid":2225557,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高院法官包華禮縱容警魔非禮示威者於2020年度喜獲林鄭授勳","createTime":"2020-10-01T11:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T13:01:02.000Z","uid":26770,"like":21,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"89bce476ad253f615713e82bab2cc2f946041c7e","tid":2225557,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:57:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20170421/LML7X2T6ZRZKSQB2HL7UCFNCG4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20170421%2FLML7X2T6ZRZKSQB2HL7UCFNCG4%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w16NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=8ac9b85e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20170421%2FLML7X2T6ZRZKSQB2HL7UCFNCG4%2F&h=5a6762dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20170421/LML7X2T6ZRZKSQB2HL7UCFNCG4/</a><br />\n<br />\n城大生控警毆打非禮(粗暴抓下體) 索償1,200萬<br />\n高院法官包華禮竟屈受害人的控告係示威行為,叫受害人有意見就去上街唔好去法院告警察"},{"pid":"61795b78300e0a088340d0211f9e93969675c27f","tid":2225557,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:00:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201001/26/P201001260169.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201001%2F26%2FP201001260169.htm&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w16NZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=2e73ef93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201001/26/P201001260169.htm</a><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">吳重儀同期<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n委任司法人員<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n下稿代司法機構發出：<br />\n<br />\n  司法機構今日（一月二十六日）宣布兩項有關高等法院和區域法院的任命。<br />\n <br />\n  任命包括一位高等法院原訟法庭法官和一位區域法院法官。有關任命由行政長官根據司法人員推薦委員會的推薦而作出。兩項任命均於二○一○年二月一日起生效。<br />\n<br />\n高等法院原訟法庭法官<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n  包華禮資深大律師獲委任為高等法院原訟法庭法官。<br />\n<br />\n區域法院法官<br />\n－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n  彭寶琴獲委任為區域法院法官。<br />\n<br />\n  其他的司法人員任命，將於適當時間公布。<br />\n<br />\n  獲委任的法官和司法人員簡歷如下：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>包華禮資深大律師</strong><br />\n<br />\n  包華禮資深大律師於一九五三年在香港出生。一九七六年在香港大學取得法學士學位。一九七八年及一九九一年分別在香港和澳洲獲大律師資格。二○○八年獲委任為資深大律師。他自一九七八年起私人執業。<br />\n<br />\n彭寶琴<br />\n<br />\n  彭寶琴於一九六二年在香港出生。一九八五年在香港大學取得社會科學學士學位。一九九四年及二○○一年在香港大學分別取得法學專業證書及法學碩士學位。一九九四年在香港獲大律師資格。一九九五年加入前律政署出任檢察官，一九九八年晉升為高級政府律師。二○○七年獲委任為副首席政府律師。<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n２０１０年１月２６日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間１６時４７分"},{"pid":"576d8cbda28fe7cb663baec356e76397227f1093","tid":2225557,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c058905c7a8c87720386d56eb3523d635cd05c","tid":2225557,"uid":26770,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"97後授勳係人格證明<br />\n證明人格有嚴重瑕疵"},{"pid":"147b92ee711073a5af692e8157d660b8844d7808","tid":2225557,"uid":233193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"人渣證明勳章"},{"pid":"08b3de7077f0cdef87fdfa483ba842a9ae03263b","tid":2225557,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:03:45.000Z","msg":"omdb<br />\n<br />\n而家班飯民重投曬共"},{"pid":"165f11a718b668d68f8a0db5d3d55dd4e6eb7203","tid":2225557,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"08b3de7077f0cdef87fdfa483ba842a9ae03263b","tid":2225557,"uid":78769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:03:45.000Z","msg":"omdb<br />\n<br />\n而家班飯民重投曬共"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T12:06:05.000Z","msg":"花生台班撚樣仲話香港法官只係立場稍保守<br />\n<br />\n1)狗方口供明顯矛盾,吳重儀,鄭念慈照屈示威者坐監<br />\n2)法院簽搜查令迫害荃灣警局輪姦案受害人,香港所有議員/主流傳媒扮盲"},{"pid":"767ca12b6d5906ac752b1a128a5df435747f9c7b","tid":2225557,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"165f11a718b668d68f8a0db5d3d55dd4e6eb7203"